{
  "stem": "23572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He went-- he went to his business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But nothing happened to his business because he didn't-- he didn't have a store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a wholesaler, up on-- up on the second floor, somewhere, in the-- in the business district.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anybody that had stores was just-- glass was smashed, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he came right home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we just-- and we just-- we said, stay put.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We stayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's what I remember about Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, plenty of-- first of all, you couldn't-- you couldn't go-- a lot, a lot of stores, the department stores, for example, had the sign 'Jews'-- 'Jews not allowed' or 'not desired.' You know, you couldn't go-- you couldn't go to, like, a Broadway or, or a Robinson, or whatever, just Macey's, you know.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing you could go in was some-- there were some Jewish-- there was some Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, you could go in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of stores, even smallest stores, had signs that-- 'Jews not wanted.' You could not go to the theater.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could not go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, you couldn't even go to the public park.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to have a little section left for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was called the 'Judenpark,' you know, the Jew Park.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I used to go there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A lot of-- a lot of signs of anti-Semitism that you-- I experienced that, sure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, they explained to us what was going on, and they--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, it's, it's-- there's people in power now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're, you know, in the government, which is anti-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're persecuting Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, you know, never-- nobody ever expected things to happen what happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
